OL,11,Fbattle will involve claims of both
OL,12,Fprivate and public nuisance by people
OL,13,Fliving in the wider area surrounding
OL,14,Fthe River Wye, encompassing parts of
OL,15,FPowys, Herefordshire, and
OL,16,FMonmouthshire.
