OL,3,CChicken producer denies claims their
OL,4,Cfarm manure is polluting the River Wye
OL,6,FThe claimants range from local
OL,7,Fproperty owners to members of the
OL,8,Fcommunity engaging in outdoor and
OL,9,Fleisure activities, all of whom say
OL,10,Fthey have been adversely affected by
OL,11,Fthe pollution.JAccording to the law
OL,12,Ffirm, the issue stems from the rapid
OL,13,Fexpansion of the chicken industry in
OL,14,Fthe area, with Avara Foods allegedly
OL,15,Fresponsible for the majority of the
OL,16,Fchicken population in the River Wye
OL,17,Fcatchment.
