OL,3,CChicken producer denies claims their
OL,4,Cfarm manure is polluting the River Wye
OL,6,FThe high-intensity farming required to
OL,7,Fmeet the demands of large
OL,8,Fsupermarkets, like Tesco, has led to a
OL,9,Fsignificant increase in phosphorous-
OL,10,Frich manure seeping into the river,
OL,11,Fcausing harmful algal blooms and
OL,12,Freducing water quality.JThis lawsuit
OL,13,Fis not the first of its kind for
OL,14,FAvara's parent company, Cargill Plc,
OL,15,Fwhich faced similar allegations in the
OL,16,FUS for polluting the Illinois River.
