OL,3,CChicken producer denies claims their
OL,4,Cfarm manure is polluting the River Wye
OL,6,FLeigh Day says it is determined to
OL,7,Fhold Avara Foods accountable for the
OL,8,Falleged environmental damage and is
OL,9,Fseeking substantial compensation for
OL,10,Fthose affected, while also pushing for
OL,11,Factions to prevent further pollution
OL,12,Fof the River Wye.
OL,14,FLeigh Day partner Oliver Holland said:
OL,15,F"We consider that the significant
OL,16,Fdecline in the health of the River Wye
OL,17,Fover the last few years is clearly
OL,18,Flinked to the significant increase in
OL,19,Fintensive poultry farming in the main
OL,20,Fbrought about by Avara Foods.
