OL,3,CChicken producer denies claims their
OL,4,Cfarm manure is polluting the River Wye
OL,6,F"This is a year-old, opportunistic
OL,7,Fattempt to profit from a serious
OL,8,Fenvironmental issue. It has no merit
OL,9,Fand is not supported by evidence or
OL,10,Fexpert opinion. It ignores the long-
OL,11,Fstanding use of phosphate-rich
OL,12,Ffertiliser by arable farms as well as
OL,13,Fthe clear scientific data showing the
OL,14,Fissue of excess phosphorus
OL,15,Fconsiderably pre-dates the growth of
OL,16,Fpoultry farms in the Wye catchment.
OL,18,F"We are confident that there is no
OL,19,Fcase to defend but, if forced to do
OL,20,Fso, we would pursue Leigh Day to
OL,21,Frecover any costs we incur."
